{
  "number": 83,
  "name": "سُورَةُ المُطَفِّفِينَ",
  "englishName": "Al-Mutaffifin",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "Woe unto the defrauders:",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "Those who when they take the measure from mankind demand it full,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "But if they measure unto them or weight for them, they cause them loss.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Do such (men) not consider that they will be raised again",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "Unto an Awful Day,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "The day when (all) mankind stand before the Lord of the Worlds?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Nay, but the record of the vile is in Sijjin -",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "Ah! what will convey unto thee what Sijjin is! -",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "A written record.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "Woe unto the repudiators on that day!",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Those who deny the Day of Judgment",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "Which none denieth save each criminal transgressor,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "Who, when thou readest unto him Our revelations, saith: (Mere) fables of the men of old.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "Nay, but that which they have earned is rust upon their hearts.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Nay, but surely on that day they will be covered from (the mercy of) their Lord.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "Then lo! they verily will burn in hell,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "And it will be said (unto them): This is that which ye used to deny.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "Nay, but the record of the righteous is in 'Illiyin -",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "Ah, what will convey unto thee what 'Illiyin is! -",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "A written record,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "Attested by those who are brought near (unto their Lord).",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "Lo! the righteous verily are in delight,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "On couches, gazing,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "Thou wilt know in their faces the radiance of delight.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "They are given to drink of a pure wine, sealed,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "Whose seal is musk - for this let (all) those strive who strive for bliss -",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And mixed with water of Tasnim,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "A spring whence those brought near (to Allah) drink.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "Lo! the guilty used to laugh at those who believed,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And wink one to another when they passed them;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "And when they returned to their own folk, they returned jesting;",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And when they saw them they said: Lo! these have gone astray.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "Yet they were not sent as guardians over them.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "This day it is those who believe who have the laugh of disbelievers,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "On high couches, gazing.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "Are not the disbelievers paid for what they used to do?",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}